flowchart LR
  %% Diagram 45: Order History and Analytics Query Flow

  Buyer[Buyer UI]
  Vendor[Vendor UI]
  Admin[Admin UI]

  Query[Query API Layer\nRead-only endpoints]
  Authz[Role and scope authorization]
  Cache[(Redis/Materialized Cache)]
  Read[(PostgreSQL Read Replica)]
  Search[(Search/Denormalized Views)]
  Assemble[Assemble response DTO]
  Trace[Attach trace id and latency markers]
  NoWrite[No write-model mutation allowed]

  CacheHit{Cache hit?}
  SlowPath[Fallback read path\nwith higher latency]
  SourceOK{Read source available?}
  Stale[Serve stale snapshot with degraded flag]

  Buyer --> Query
  Vendor --> Query
  Admin --> Query

  Query --> Authz --> CacheHit
  CacheHit -- Yes --> Cache --> Assemble
  CacheHit -- No --> SourceOK
  SourceOK -- Yes --> Read --> Search --> SlowPath --> Assemble
  SourceOK -- No --> Stale --> Assemble

  Assemble --> Trace
  Trace --> Buyer
  Trace --> Vendor
  Trace --> Admin

  Query -.enforces.-> NoWrite
